Package: QuadST
Type: Package
Title: A Powerful and Robust Approach for Identifying Cellâ€“Cell
        Interaction-Changed Genes on Spatially Resolved Transcriptomics
Version: 0.1.0
Author: SongLab  
Maintainer: The package maintainer <song.xiaoyu@duke-nus.edu.sg>
Description: The goal of QuadST is on the robust and powerful identification of interaction-changed genes (ICGs) for cell-type-pair-specific interactions using single-cell spatially resolved transcriptome data. QuadST can be a useful tool to discover genes and regulatory processes involved in cell-type-pair-specific interactions underlying human health and disease. 
